=========================================================================

Surge Trim Tuning

- Make surge-only travel straight with minimal X drift and minimal Y rotation

Result:
- Needed to set Right Surge Multiplier = 1.457
- Left Surge Multiplier stayed at 1.0

With this trim:
- Surge-only motion became almost pure Z motion
- Position X no longer drifted significantly
- Rotation Y no longer increased significantly

- Horizontal surge motion is now trimmed and stable

Current surge trim:
- Left Surge Multiplier = 1.0
- Right Surge Multiplier = 1.457

